{"tid":344183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港產巨肺小公主射lin直接晉身AGT直播回合!","createTime":"2017-08-02T05:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T15:31:53.000Z","uid":35504,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf724f1e7d326c2b43db0761dd965a0d2af723a","tid":344183,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"美國選秀節目《全美一叮》今季突然成為港人的焦點，全因代表香港的「9歲小巨肺」譚芷昀Celine妹妹在節目中初次登場已一鳴驚人，一首Celine Dion的《My Heart Will Go On》，令她頓成焦點所在。而香港時間今天早上8點，Celine於第二輪賽事翻唱男歌手Michael Bolton的《How Am I Supposed to Live Without You》，並得到評判按下「Golden Buzzer」直送準決賽，成為首個獲得此殊榮的港人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/109185/-%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%AE-%E8%AD%9A%E8%8A%B7%E6%98%80%E6%88%90%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%8C%89%E9%88%95-%E8%A9%95%E5%88%A4-%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E6%8A%8A%E4%BD%A0%E5%B8%B6%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%2F109185%2F-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258F%25AE-%25E8%25AD%259A%25E8%258A%25B7%25E6%2598%2580%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%258C%2589%25E9%2588%2595-%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%258A%258A%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25AE%25B6&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml454f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=668cddc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/109185/-%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%AE-%E8%AD%9A%E8%8A%B7%E6%98%80%E6%88%90%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%8C%89%E9%88%95-%E8%A9%95%E5%88%A4-%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E6%8A%8A%E4%BD%A0%E5%B8%B6%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T9ZbP7Fkzug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT9ZbP7Fkzug&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml454f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a8a81a95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T9ZbP7Fkzug</a>"},{"pid":"254b81d88821753b50122afa26b0a012a1172c3f","tid":344183,"uid":57331,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"個topic已經可以叫fbi"},{"pid":"e5394ed67d1c8e7b73c042c634d14c5e521d4faa","tid":344183,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"去年Celine妹妹與爸爸一起簽約到蕭定一旗下，當時蕭生已打算將Celine妹妹打造成最年輕的紅館歌手，打破G.E.M. 鄧紫棋的紀錄。事隔一年，Celine妹妹已是國際級樂壇新貴，重提紅館開騷一事，蕭定一接受《香港01》訪問時表示：「其實未有《AGT》呢件事前已經一直計劃緊，而家Celine參加咗《America&rsquo;s Got Talent》之後，當然更希望可以做到一個慈善演唱會。始終小朋友喺呢一個階段，希望唔係一個商業嘅行為。不過大家都知道紅館嘅期係好難攞，盡快申請到紅館期再同大家宣布，有時候有呢個構思都未必可以付諸實行。」<br />\n<br />\n開紅館演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73eaa796807c7d876bb85bce6a5877d918b8120","tid":344183,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"理撚得你"},{"pid":"6ae98199e634c118373a60293a48bb670adf0cf0","tid":344183,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"收幾錢開post?"},{"pid":"2116772f6eab2aff48426e3cf90b411bb0c92815","tid":344183,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"😂😂😂😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"bfc691ff1da3ab78cfa43409bd406fdd6f510565","tid":344183,"uid":24737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去年Celine妹妹與爸爸一起簽約到蕭定一旗下，當時蕭生已打算將Celine妹妹打造成最年輕的紅館歌手，打破G.E.M. 鄧紫棋的紀錄。事隔一年，Celine妹妹已是國際級樂壇新貴，重提紅館開騷一事，蕭定一接受《香港01》訪問時表示：「其實未有《AGT》呢件事前已經一直計劃緊，而家Celine參加咗《America&rsquo;s Got Talent》之後，當然更希望可以做到一個慈善演唱會。始終小朋友喺呢一個階段，希望唔係一個商業嘅行為。不過大家都知道紅館嘅期係好難攞，盡快申請到紅館期再同大家宣布，有時候有呢個構思都未必可以付諸實行。」<br />\n<br />\n開紅館演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿豬阿狗都話要紅館"},{"pid":"de557c4c1e9eb8609309dd008e